Detailed Description

This sub block indicates fault in analog supplies or LDO short circuit condition. Once a fault is detected the functionality cannot be resumed from then on and the sensor needs to be re-started. This Async Event is generated with SB-ID RL_DEV_AE_MSS_VMON_ERROR_STATUS_SB.
